author: lgo
msg: Implement ra_serf progress feedback. This requires serf@r1170 to build
(svn_ra_serf__progress): New callback function that's passed to the serf
library, and passes any incoming progress updates to the subversion callback
(svn_ra_serf__conn_setup): Use the new socket bucket creation function
provided by serf, which automatically initiates the progress feedback
(struct svn_ra_serf__session_t): add new member variables for progress
